Class ServiceCatalogRegistry

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.svr.cat.ServiceCatalogRegistry
public class ServiceCatalogRegistry
extends Object

A ServiceCatalogRegistry provides a placeholder for all the map services loaded automatically from a mapservices.xml file or added by users through its APIs.
